Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:48.51,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H000000&\3c&HD1D2D1&}泪痕已经干涸  这不是真的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:52.18,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}“为什么？”
