Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:21.00,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H83653F&\2c&HB49C5D&}开心得在飞  伤心地流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:24.13,OPEDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDEA0F8&}“都是你的不对”
